<!DOCTYPE html> <html> <head> <meta charset="UTF-8"> <title>Happy 1 Month Anniversary ❤️</title> <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Great+Vibes&family=Poppins:wght@300;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> <style> body{ background:#FFD1DC; font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif; text-align:center; color:white; overflow:hidden; } /* container */ .container{ margin-top:80px; position:relative; z-index:2; } h1{ font-size:45px; font-family:'Great Vibes',cursive; } h2{ font-size:35px; color:#ff2e63; text-shadow:0 0 10px white,0 0 20px white; } p{ font-size:20px; width:70%; margin:auto; } button{ padding:12px 25px; font-size:18px; border:none; border-radius:20px; background:white; color:#ff4b6e; cursor:pointer; margin-top:30px; } .hidden{ display:none; margin-top:20px; font-size:22px; } /* falling animation */ @keyframes fall{ to{ transform:translateY(100vh); opacity:0; } } .fall{ position:fixed; top:-20px; animation:fall linear; z-index:1; } /* glowing love animation */ .loveScreen{ position:fixed; top:50%; left:50%; transform:translate(-50%,-50%); font-size:60px; font-family:'Great Vibes',cursive; color:#ff2e63; text-shadow: 0 0 10px white, 0 0 20px white, 0 0 40px pink, 0 0 80px pink; display:none; z-index:5; animation:pulse 2s infinite; } @keyframes pulse{ 0%{transform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1);} 50%{transform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1.15);} 100%{transform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1);} } </style> </head> <body> <audio id="bgMusic" loop preload="auto"> <source src="song.mp3" type="audio/mpeg"> </audio> <div class="container"> <h1>Happy 1 Monthhhh Anniversaryyyyyyyyyyyyy 💕</h1> <h2>Kushu ❤️ Tanu</h2> <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/40/Rose_flower.jpg/320px-Rose_flower.jpg" width="200"> <p> its alrewdsyy 1 monthhhhh. and so much more to goo.... i lovee u so muchhhh.... 💖 </p> <button onclick="showMessage(); playMusic(); showLove()">Click this if you miss me 💌</button> <div class="hidden" id="message"> kushhuuuuu.... i know its only been 1 month still we have seen fights and cries 💕 but one thing is sure we are not gonna leave each other 🧿 i can see our potential... what we are and what we can become 😘 even if times are hard right now i'm always with you 🫂💕 </div> <p style="margin-top:40px"> yourssss,<br> <b>Tanu 🤭😘</b> </p> </div> <div class="loveScreen" id="loveText"> ❤️ I Love You Kushu ❤️ </div> <script> function showMessage(){ document.getElementById("message").style.display="block"; } function playMusic(){ const music=document.getElementById("bgMusic"); music.volume=0.7; music.play().catch(()=>{}); } function showLove(){ document.getElementById("loveText").style.display="block"; } /* falling love letters & tulips */ function createFall(){ const item=document.createElement("div"); item.innerHTML=Math.random()>0.5 ? "💌":"🌷"; item.classList.add("fall"); item.style.left=Math.random()*window.innerWidth+"px"; item.style.fontSize=(20+Math.random()*30)+"px"; item.style.animationDuration=(4+Math.random()*4)+"s"; document.body.appendChild(item); setTimeout(()=>{ item.remove(); },8000); } setInterval(createFall,300); </script> </body> </html> 
